WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.680
Look! There's little ducks!

00:06.240 --> 00:09.500
Six little ducks that I once knew,

00:10.000 --> 00:12.640
fat ones, skinny ones, fair ones too.

00:12.680 --> 00:16.340
But the one little duck with the feather on his back,

00:16.900 --> 00:20.000
he led the others with the quack quack quack.

00:20.180 --> 00:23.380
Quack quack quack, quack quack quack.

00:23.700 --> 00:26.820
He led the others with the quack quack quack.

00:28.120 --> 00:30.000
Here we go!

00:30.920 --> 00:33.740
Down to the river they would go.

00:34.260 --> 00:37.040
Wibble wobble, wibble wobble to and fro.

00:37.100 --> 00:40.760
But the one little duck with the feather on his back,

00:41.520 --> 00:44.300
he led the others with the quack quack quack.

00:44.460 --> 00:47.700
Quack quack quack, quack quack quack.

00:47.960 --> 00:50.920
He led the others with the quack quack quack.

00:54.580 --> 00:58.300
Home by the river they would come.

00:58.500 --> 01:01.380
Wibble wobble, wibble wobble ho hum hum.

01:01.380 --> 01:05.040
But the one little duck with the feather on his back,

01:05.620 --> 01:08.260
he led the others with the quack quack quack.

01:08.680 --> 01:12.020
Quack quack quack, quack quack quack.

01:12.300 --> 01:16.200
He led the others with the quack quack quack.

01:17.620 --> 01:18.960
Quack quack quack.

01:22.160 --> 01:23.560
Meow.

